      "id": "PopularPost267653",
      "post_content": "Too few cards are made that involve giving the opponent the option of paying mana to do something about it.  \n  \nI like the style of gameplay that encourages (kind of feels like DragonBallZ or the Priori Incantatem effect in Harry Potter: have a mana/ki battle to see who can pump more power into the clusterbomb you made on the battlefield, thus gaining control of the game, without actually exhausting yourself into oblivion...unless you at least take out your opponent too)  \n  \n4x [Daze](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Daze)  \n4x [Mana Leak](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Leak)  \n4x [Spell Pierce](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spell Pierce)  \n4x [Slow Motion](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Slow Motion)  \n  \n  \nsounds like a good deck :)",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost267653\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Too few cards are made that involve giving the opponent the option of paying mana to do something about it.<br/><br/>I like the style of gameplay that encourages (kind of feels like DragonBallZ or the Priori Incantatem effect in Harry Potter: have a mana/ki battle to see who can pump more power into the clusterbomb you made on the battlefield, thus gaining control of the game, without actually exhausting yourself into oblivion...unless you at least take out your opponent too)<br/><br/>4x <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Daze\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Daze\">Daze</a><br/>4x <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mana Leak\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Leak\">Mana Leak</a><br/>4x <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spell Pierce\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spell Pierce\">Spell Pierce</a><br/>4x <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Slow Motion\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Slow Motion\">Slow Motion</a><br/><br/><br/>sounds like a good deck :)</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '267653'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46041\">DarthParallax</span>\r\n                                (9/1